    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean... what does \"taking a step back\" even look like? because it feels like every time i try to just exist, the cost is just too high. like, it's not even about a break, it's more like i'm just done with the whole struggle of it. it feels so heavy and pointless sometimes.",
